message.body: Heeeeyyyyyy! Are we still up for Friday?
Hey. I'm good for Friday if you are! It'll be nice cause my midterms will be over.
Even better! Whoop whoop!!! Time to celebrate...with a risqu√© movie hahah.
Haha. Didn't you see it already though?
We don't have to see the movie if you did. We can do something else.
No, I was waiting for you to see it.
Oh coolio!
Ohhhh you mean the Facebook thing? No, I babysat so Xuan could go see it with Tom.
But she missed it hahah.
Oh no!!! Okay! Sounds good to me. Friday!!!
I'm checking out movie times and they have evening showings at 7:45 and then 10. Preference?
Wanna do 10 and then we can go somewhere for dinner around 7ish?
Awesome! It's on like Sauvignon!!! Whoo.
Haha. Sounds good. Should we asked sam and Eden if they wanna go, or just make it a you-me thang?
I remember bringing it up when we hung out before and Eden said she's going to wait for it to come out on DVD and I remember Sam not being a fan. But we could ask anyways?
Ehhhhh. Me-you date. We don't have enough anyway.
True that! How are midterms going?
Not too great. Have one thurs and fri. Lots of info. Not enough time.
Eck, That sounds like a midterm. But you're Jenny, and you know you're going to kill it!
Haha. Chemistry is tomorrow. As long as I can get through that, we'll be okay. Micro is mostly memorization so I'll have all day tomorrow for that.
Haha thank you!
You so have it under control! It'll be like a bandaid. Good luck!!!
